products.title: Coconut Bar Soap
products.body_html:
Coconut Bar Soap is perfect for everyday cleansing. It's handmade in small batches using traditional methods and gentle enough for daily use. A more natural alternative to commercial soap.

Features:
  • Handmade in small batches with organic coconut oil and shea
  • No parabens, synthetic fragrances, or chemicals
  • Gentle enough for daily use
  • Suitable for sensitive skin
  • Vegan friendly and cruelty-free
